{"tid":1441550,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"文宣圖 直接攻屋邨","createTime":"2019-08-10T16:35:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T11:07:19.000Z","uid":53808,"like":86,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"8a0dc5e5685ee302cb75b847854592e356c4a827","tid":1441550,"uid":53808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T16:35:37.000Z","msg":"運動發展到今日<br />\n相信大家開始理解到沉醉同溫層嘅危險 <br />\n<br />\n而家target藍絲嘅文宣圖已經陸續整緊/整咗<br />\n雖然網軍都努力散緊貨<br />\n但仲有一班人係唔上網<br />\n如果我哋<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">印出嚟貼喺屋邨</span>有冇得諗？<br />\n<br />\n呢個同連儂牆係兩回事 <br />\n我哋要反滲透藍絲<br />\n就要用<span style=\"color: red;\">跟藍絲思路整嘅圖 貼喺藍絲屋企 日鳩日迫佢哋睇</span><br />\n<br />\n當然呢個行動有一定危險 <br />\n小則畀心水清藍絲當場圍屌 大則喺分貨過程被篤灰<br />\n<br />\n巴絲信得過我嘅 tg我一齊傾傾點搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果有人做緊 由個post沉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nTg: savedad"},{"pid":"75f5b70e518d8b98550952e5621445ec4d62ef36","tid":1441550,"uid":65166,"like":52,"dislike":0,"score":52,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T16:39:57.000Z","msg":"邊有用<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d31730b58179f09bfb7f44e4202d31835f58e7c","tid":1441550,"uid":53808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:01:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b121510c463450517b969a89db14d28617acabd5","tid":1441550,"uid":47924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:02:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"987663c9c4a3e3a9718a8bfb327d5f6fe18903c6","tid":1441550,"uid":30767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:04:38.000Z","msg":"無知一問<br />\nzip傳單入信箱有冇犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c47c16dee86450a509ff00e308a8a7ce662ad74","tid":1441550,"uid":67231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:04:50.000Z","msg":"